      "Text": "Security update for gnutls",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for gnutls fixes the following issues:\n\n- CVE-2025-14831: excessive resource consumption when verifying  specially crafted malicious certificates containing\n  a large number of name constraints and subject alternative names (SANs) (bsc#1257960).\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
    },
